EX Abilities


Filling the Recast Gauge
• The gauge will fill with each turn (including enemies) in battle. How the gauge fills varies by EX Ability.
　Also, the gauge will fill differently depending on the turn rate of selected actions.
　
• A character possessing an EX Ability will see his or her gauge fill more quickly by using abilities.
　*Abilites transformed from the regular BRV Attack and HP Attack are exempt.
　* Even if an ability is triggered more than once in a single turn, it will only fill the gauge for one turn's worth.
*How easily the gauge fills when using abilities varies by character.




*A Limit Break Effect can be learned by Limit Breaking a weapon with an Affinity Ability that allows use of an EX Ability.
